text.tspan: Electricity production in the United Kingdom
Electricity generated in the UK, plus net electricity imports (imports minus exports). "Other renewables" include
bioenergy, geothermal, wave, and tidal sources.
Data source: Ember (2025); Energy Institute - Statistical Review of World Energy (2024); Department for Business, Energy & Industrial
